Prerequisites for all test cases is the definition of 10 orders.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 1
Use case        : admin order management
Scenario name   : modify order
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Select the link "Ordini" and then show all orders.
5. Select an order and select the link "Modifica".
6. Put a string in the text box "Nota" and press the button Salva.

7. Repeat the same from details order.

Expected results:

1. After step 6 and 7 the order is correctly updated.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 2
Use case        : admin order management
Scenario name   : change state
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Select the link "Ordini" and then show all orders.
5. Select an order and select the link "Modifica".
6. Change the state of the order and press the button Salva.

7. Repeat the same from details order.

Expected results:

1. After step 6 and 7 the order is correctly updated.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 3
Use case        : admin order management
Scenario name   : update more than one order
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Select the link "Ordini" and then show all orders.
5. Select two orders and select the link "Modifica".
6. Change whatever field and press the button Salva.

Expected results:

1. After step 6 the orders are correctly updated.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 4
Use case        : admin order management
Scenario name   : delete order
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Select the link "Ordini" and then show all orders.
5. Select an order and select the link "Cancella".

6. repeat the same scenario selecting more than one order.

Expected results:

1. After step 5 the order is removed from the system.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 5
Use case        : admin order management
Scenario name   : tracking order
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Select the link "Ordini" and then show all orders.
5. Select an order and select the link "Tracking".
6. Select a shipping company and update tracking text field.

7. repeat the same scenario selecting more than one order.

Expected results:

1. After step 6 and 7 the order is correctly updated.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 6
Use case        : admin order management
Scenario name   : send reminder
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Select the link "Ordini" and then show all orders.
5. Select an order and select the link "Invio Promemoria Pagamento".

6. repeat the same scenario selecting more than one order.

Expected results:

1. After step 5 and 6 the mail is correctly sent.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scenario number : 7
Use case        : admin order management
Scenario name   : download csv
Description     :

1. Connect through a web browser to Bazaar system.
2. Select the "Login" link.
3. Login as administrator.
4. Select the link "Ordini" and then show all orders.
5. Select the link "Scarica tutti i CSV".

Expected results:

1. Verify file downloaded.
